  "concepts": [
    "Question words carry an accent: qué, dónde, cómo, cuándo, por qué",
    "Word order in questions is flexible — rising intonation can turn a statement into a question",
    "¿Qué? = What? ¿Dónde? = Where? ¿Cómo? = How?",
    "¿Por qué? = Why? (two words, with accent and space)"
  ],
